snippet.title: Fight of Gods - Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Today, Fight of Gods ascends from Early Access. The full version of the notorious fighting game that features gods, holy spirits and mythological characters from around the globe and throughout history, is out now on Steam.

http://store.steampowered.com/app/612930/Fight_of_Gods/ 

Come chat to us on our PQube Discord server! 
https://discord.gg/xHS7MnU

#FightOfGods
